These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, december
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, sunflower
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, cape-cod
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, prince, aristoff
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, western, drama
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, cape-cod-climbing, drawing
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is the farmhouse house##1
 5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsrose is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is between the prince-smoker and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
11. the person who growsrose is the aristoff-smoker##1
12. the person who growssunflower is the person who's hobby is cape-cod-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Birthday          | august   | december            | may     |
| Flower           | rose | sunflower | marigold |
| House   | ranch-style      | cape-cod               | farmhouse        |
| Cigar           | aristoff        | chaman         | prince   |
| Movie-Genre         | drama     | western      | disaster       |
| Hobby     | drawing        | cape-cod-climbing              | hiking       |

