.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
City: venice, prague, marseilles
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, videographer, designer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, may, july
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, prince, tiparillo
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, russian, polish
3 different games are played: backgammon, domino, poker
 1. the doctor is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 3. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
 4. the designer is the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the person playing poker is between the doctor and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 6. the italian is between the videographer and the person playing backgammon##2
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is the russian##1
 8. the doctor is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
10. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| City      | venice | prague | marseilles        |
| Job          | videographer   | designer    | doctor        |
| Birthday   | february    | may | july |
| Cigar   | tiparillo   | vegafina  | prince         |
| Nationality           | polish    | italian | russian       |
| Game     | domino   | poker    | backgammon  |

