.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, soccer, skateboarding
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, march
3 different games are played: monopoly, whist, scrabble
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bongani, chaman
City: hamburg, colone, london
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, amaryllis, begonia
 1. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 2. the chaman-smoker is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 4. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person playing whist and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 9. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
10. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing whist is the bongani-smoker##1
12. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
13. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Sport      | soccer        | water-polo     | skateboarding          |
| Birthday          | december     | august | march    |
| Game         | whist    | monopoly  | scrabble |
