.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, grey, coral
There 3 different types of food: grapes, lemon, cucumber
City: colone, venice, hamburg
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, train
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, writer, fisherman
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, january
 1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 3. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person eating cucumber##2
 6. the writer is on the far right##1
 7. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 8. the person traveling to colone is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the dancer is in an odd position##4
10. the fisherman is in an even position##4
11. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person eating cucumber is the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Color      | grey  | coral      | purple        |
| Food         | cucumber   | grapes     | lemon |
| City   | colone | hamburg | venice     |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | motorbike         | train         |
| Job   | dancer   | fisherman     | writer      |
| Birthday         | july  | january     | april         |

