 1. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
 2. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
 3. the person eating cauliflower is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who likes lilac is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who likes emerald is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the craftsman house##1
10. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
11. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
