 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the modern house##3
 6. the gothic-revival house is the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |
