.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-17::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, subway
City: nizza, colone, edinburgh
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower, begonia
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, nurse, dressmaker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, scientific
3 different games are played: chess, domino, whist
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 2. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
 3. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
 4. the nurse is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 5. the security-guard is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the nurse is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
12. the person driving the subway is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
