.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
City: nizza, boston, hannover
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, action, crime
3 different games are played: go, monopoly, scrabble
3 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, pony
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, apricot, grey
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, april, november
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the owner of the turtle is between the person watching action movies and the person who likes grey##2
3. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the owner of the goat is the person watching crime movies##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person playing go and the person traveling to hannover##2
9. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| City      | hannover    | boston           | nizza         |
| Movie-Genre         | crime   | zombie             | action  |
| Game           | scrabble  | monopoly | go |
| Pet   | goat      | turtle              | pony      |
| Color   | grey | apricot             | green     |
| Birthday         | april   | february           | november      |

