.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, journalist, lawyer
3 different games are played: backgammon, whist, mah-jongg
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, lily
House: modern, cottage, art-deco
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, martial-arts
 1. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
 2. the lawyer is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left or right of the modern house##3
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 8. the person who growslily is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person playing whist is the journalist##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| Job          | journalist    | lawyer  | bartender   |
| Game   | whist      | backgammon  | mah-jongg  |
| Flower   | marigold | dahlia  | lily |
| House           | cottage     | modern   | art-deco   |
| Beverage         | almond-milk  | tea | soy-milk |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts   | adventure      | sports  |

