.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: billiard, domino, scrabble
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, ambient
3 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, hedgehog
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, turquise, yellow
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, december
City: new-york, edinburgh, hannover
 1. the fan of folk is the person traveling to hannover##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 5. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
10. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Game          | domino     | scrabble   | billiard     |
| Music-Genre         | ambient | classical   | folk  |
| Pet           | turtle   | hedgehog | snake   |
| Color   | ebony    | turquise       | yellow    |
| Birthday   | december        | september    | october   |
| City         | edinburgh      | new-york     | hannover |

 